    "row_data": "{\"id\": \"tmem_122\", \"role\": \"lead\", \"notes\": \"Sarah Whitcomb leads daily close blocker triage for managed clients, including follow-up on bank feed exceptions and cash posting delays tied to reconciliation items such as BL-18FFAE0E20D0 on 117000 Allowance for Doubtful Accounts.\", \"title\": \"Outsourced accounting operations lead\", \"team_id\": \"linear_5477c0808ac2\", \"user_id\": \"linear_2e7b3ea28766\", \"created_at\": \"2026-03-03T09:26:56Z\", \"start_date\": \"2026-03-01T08:00:00\", \"updated_at\": \"2026-03-03T04:26:56-05:00\"}",
    "source": "linear.linear_team_memberships"
  },
  {
    "row_data": "{\"id\": \"tmem_124\", \"role\": \"member\", \"notes\": \"Michael Reyes supports accounts payable workflow reviews across managed clients and monitors approval bottlenecks, including vendor items like VEN-019-583136 pending approval and VEN-012-211225 approved but awaiting processing review.\", \"title\": \"AP workflow standardization specialist\", \"team_id\": \"linear_5477c0808ac2\", \"user_id\": \"linear_6ef0fc68abd7\", \"created_at\": \"2026-03-03T09:42:37Z\", \"start_date\": \"2026-03-04T09:00:00\", \"updated_at\": \"2026-03-08T06:22:00-04:00\"}",
    "source": "linear.linear_team_memberships"
  },
  {
    "row_data": "{\"id\": \"tmem_123\", \"role\": \"member\", \"notes\": \"Lisa Park was assigned into the legacy bookkeeping cleanup and opening balance remediation rotation, with focus on clearing stale reconciling items and documenting support around BL-3E4ED5B5B9BA in 131000 Prepaid Software Subscriptions.\", \"title\": \"Bookkeeping remediation senior\", \"team_id\": \"linear_5477c0808ac2\", \"user_id\": \"linear_4d9e2b202532\", \"created_at\": \"2026-03-10T10:39:22Z\", \"start_date\": \"2026-03-10T08:30:00\", \"updated_at\": \"2026-03-15T12:09:00-04:00\"}",
    "source": "linear.linear_team_memberships"
  },
  {
    "row_data": "{\"id\": \"tmem_126\", \"role\": \"member\", \"notes\": \"Daniel Jones joined the Tuesday monthly close capacity standup rotation and assists with daily bank feed exception follow-up, especially investigation support for exc_af7274fb658844 and duplicate-entry review items escalated by seniors.\", \"title\": \"Graduate accounting analyst\", \"team_id\": \"linear_5477c0808ac2\", \"user_id\": \"persona_002\", \"created_at\": \"2026-03-03T08:46:15Z\", \"start_date\": \"2026-03-02T09:00:00\", \"updated_at\": \"2026-03-19T08:14:00-04:00\"}",
    "source": "linear.linear_team_memberships"
  },
  {
    "row_data": "{\"id\": \"tmem_125\", \"role\": \"mentor\", \"notes\": \"George McAdam provides weekly trainee work review for Daniel Jones on close support assignments, including documentation quality checks on cash postings, reconciliations, and exception summaries before partner review.\", \"title\": \"Graduate review loop mentor\", \"team_id\": \"linear_5477c0808ac2\", \"user_id\": \"persona_001\", \"created_at\": \"2026-03-03T08:49:27Z\", \"start_date\": \"2026-03-02T09:00:00\", \"updated_at\": \"2026-03-19T08:20:00-04:00\"}",
    "source": "linear.linear_team_memberships"
  },
  {
    "row_data": "{\"id\": \"tmem_127\", \"role\": \"partner_liaison\", \"notes\": \"Sarah Whitcomb acts as liaison into Tax & Compliance Delivery for client handoffs where bookkeeping delays affect filing readiness, including source document gaps and unresolved balances that could delay preparation of returns and entity filings.\", \"title\": \"Cross-team advisory liaison\", \"team_id\": \"linear_7d4b3f1127cd\", \"user_id\": \"linear_2e7b3ea28766\", \"created_at\": \"2026-04-14T10:02:53Z\", \"start_date\": \"2026-03-09T10:00:00\", \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-14T06:02:53-04:00\"}",
    "source": "linear.linear_team_memberships"
  },
  {
    "row_data": "{\"id\": \"tmem_128\", \"role\": \"member\", \"notes\": \"Lisa Park joined the audit PBC backlog burn-down effort for the retail client group and tracks support requests that intersect with journal entries such as JE-brookfield-FP-2026-05-0004 and JE-brookfield-FP-2026-05-0007.\", \"title\": \"Audit support coordinator\", \"team_id\": \"linear_7d4b3f1127cd\", \"user_id\": \"linear_4d9e2b202532\", \"created_at\": \"2026-04-14T09:42:32Z\", \"start_date\": \"2026-03-16T08:30:00\", \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-14T05:42:32-04:00\"}",
    "source": "linear.linear_team_memberships"
  },
  {
    "row_data": "{\"id\": \"tmem_129\", \"role\": \"member\", \"notes\": \"Michael Reyes was added to the multi-state annual report catch-up workstream to chase overdue client entity filings and coordinate vendor-backed items, including DocketPilot Filing Services invoice VEN-004-799133 where proof of filing is required.\", \"title\": \"Entity compliance follow-up analyst\", \"team_id\": \"linear_7d4b3f1127cd\", \"user_id\": \"linear_6ef0fc68abd7\", \"created_at\": \"2026-04-14T10:03:35Z\", \"start_date\": \"2026-03-23T09:00:00\", \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-14T07:37:00-04:00\"}",
